Package: ngramr.plus
Title: Returns Ngram Counts from Google Books Data
Version: 1.0.1
Author: David Brown [aut, cre]
Maintainer: David Brown <dwb2@andrew.cmu.edu>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Brown",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dwb2@andrew.cmu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7745-6354"))
Description: The package ngramr.plus extracts frequency data from Google Books' Ngram data: <http://storage.googleapis.com/books/ngrams/books/datasetsv2.html>. The google_ngram() function is set up to facilitate the counting of lemmas and ignore differences in capitalization. The user has control over what to combine into counts with the word_forms argument.
